2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pomeša kod, spot i pun stoji prvi prava vrata,jer sam šampio neuspjeha prv baka.

3
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
[UNKNOWN] Muzika

4
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi naši gledatelji, evo nas u Milanu, evo nas u gradu mode i gradu nogometnih uspiha.

5
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan od naših sugovornika je u ovom gradu, za jedan od ova dva kluba,

6
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] osvajao skudete ligu prvaka, svjetsko klupsko prvenstvo.

7
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Popao se na sam Monteveres nogometa.

8
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo ga pronaći da čujemo njegovu životnu priču.

9
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:26,000
[UNKNOWN] Dobro došao!

10
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,000
[UNKNOWN] Dobro došao!

11
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gorane, drago mi je vidjeti, evo nakon šest meseci zadnjih usreta je bio u Parmi.

12
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

13
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nadam se da svi dobro.

14
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro sam vas, to i meni mi je čas što sam u vašoj emisiji.

15
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] da si koje kilo nabacio?

16
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da si uspio?

17
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osam do deset kilo nabacio.

18
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Radim, igram neki mali futbal, idem s obicikl, su moji prijatelji u Dženovi, zato što smo ostali da živimo u Dženovi.

19
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, kako še si reko, nema toa adrenalina.

20
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema...

21
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki vikend sad, posle sad...

22
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki treti dan igrali utakmicu.

23
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Toa, važne utakmice.

24
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema karantina, nema pritisak.

25
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I jednostavno sam...

26
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sam se opustio da idem...

27
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I svaki dan sad da radim.

28
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad nema što pritisak, sigurno...

29
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Poedes malo...

30
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Popješ neko časvo vino...

31
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ideš i izaš e so prijatelji...

32
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] I...

33
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je...

34
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da je...

35
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da sem malo ugojio, ali...

36
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

37
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ano se vratiti na prve tvoje nogometne korake.

38
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na Strumicu.

39
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je Gradić. Koliko ima stanovnika od Priluke?

40
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Strumica je mali grad.

41
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je 60.000 stanovnika.

42
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Istočno od Makedonije.

43
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jako blizu bugarske granice.

44
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jako blizu da, bugarske granice.

45
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Blizu Petrić, bugarski i bugarski grad.

46
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ima...

47
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Futbal ima klub što postoje više 100 godina.

48
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo sad...

49
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je Belasica.

50
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je Belasica.

51
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Klub ima...

52
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je Slavio 100-godišni rođendan.

53
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo sam tamo na 10-godišno vozrast.

54
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to da ti recim kako sam pošao.

55
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema da ti se veruje.

56
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam išao na...

57
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Igrao futbal, stvarno volio samo futbala.

58
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za mene samo lopta je bila...

59
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moj hobi je bilo lopta.

60
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedina igračka je bilo.

61
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Išli smo moji drugari iz kući da živimo tamo.

62
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni govorili:

63
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ajde idemo da se opisamo za futbala."

64
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Hočeš ti da dođeš?"

65
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su bili dve godine veliki od mene.

66
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao li 12 starih od mene.

67
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dobro govorili:

68
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Doću ja da gledam kako vi trenirate."

69
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vraćam se kući.

70
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I oni počeli.

71
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo tamo.

72
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počeli.

73
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se zapisali.

74
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš ranije kako bio.

75
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Morate zapiše ime, prezime, sve to.

76
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] I počeli da trenira.

77
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja zastavamo na stranu.

78
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uzeo neke lopte.

79
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ostale lopta.

80
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ostale lopta.

81
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I govorili:

82
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Dodako oni je treniraju, ja ću..."

83
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se zavoljavam.

84
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

85
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja počeo da...

86
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] ...žongliram.

87
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da žongliram.

88
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da radim neke finte.

89
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Me vidi trener.

90
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazi.

91
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima 100 klinca imam.

92
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazi kod mene i govorim:

93
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Kako se zoveš?"

94
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja govorim:

95
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Goran."

96
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Hočeš ti da treniraš futbal?"

97
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja govorim:

98
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ne znam, treba da pitam tata i mama."

99
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš.

100
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Fenomenalno.

101
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

102
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on govorim:

103
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nemal ovde."

104
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pred svi govorim:

105
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Da pokažeš kako ti žongliraš."

106
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja me gledaj, svi djeca zastavili.

107
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja počeo.

108
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vedi kako se žonglira.

109
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako trebate svi da radite.

110
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ja kad sam počeo,

111
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] nema ja i kući to ispred.

112
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Po celi dan, znaš, kući...

113
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko si imao tad godina?

114
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao 10-11 godina.

115
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] 10-11.

116
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kon mene kući nismo živeli so...

117
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tata i...

118
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na tata njegovi...

119
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njegove mama i tata.

120
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moj deda.

121
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo imali ni pare za lopte.

122
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] mi je radio od ove novine.

123
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Od lupije novine mi je radio kao lopte

124
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] i mi daje.

125
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što ja sam hteo samo sa lopte.

126
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako počeo od ove novine.

127
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako napravio lopte i ja počeo.

128
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato tehnički sam bio...

129
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu si zapravo svoju tehniku izbrosio.

130
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Njerovatno.

131
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

132
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ulazim u trenažni proces.

133
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ulazim u trenažni proces.

134
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Belasici.

135
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Skočio ovi pioneri i kadete.

136
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odmah...

137
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Skočio...

138
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kvaliteto je bilo očitao.

139
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

140
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

141
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Igrao sam ja sa...

142
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] 2-3 godine velike.

143
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na 15 godina ušao u prvu ekipu.

144
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Belasica tad je bio u serije drugu ligu.

145
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobili smo pravenstvo i od moja generacija.

146
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo imali jednu od najbolje generacije u Makedoniji.

147
00:05:54,000 --> 00:06:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako sam dobro shvatio bio je nekakav turnir.

148
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na kojem su bili scouti Intera koji su primijetili tvoj skill.

149
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tvoj potencijalni kvalitet.

150
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

151
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Došli...

152
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije u ove generacije što sam ti pričao.

153
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] 83.

154
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] 82.

155
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,000
[UNKNOWN] Znači tvoj.

156
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gazdan na Belasice bio pokojni sa Van Čutakovski.

157
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Donao nama na turnir u Vjeređo.

158
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo bili u grupu Soperuđa, bari i jednu argentinsku ekipu.

159
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali odigrali stvarno fenomenalan turnir u Vjeređo.

160
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Postigo na tri utaknice pet gola.

161
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio puno menadžera.

162
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazili su svaki dan menadžeri u hotel.

163
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo ovaj predsednik nije htio da priča.

164
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Traži on biljone.

165
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znaš to kako kod nama odmah.

166
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

167
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govori, nije on za Inter, on je za Real Madrid, za Barcelona.

168
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odmah?

169
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

170
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima klinac od 17-16 godine.

171
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

172
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kod ti u tim trenutama, da li si imao nekoga ko ti je bio podrškan?

173
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nekoga kome si vjerovao?

174
00:06:57,000 --> 00:07:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nekakav agent, nekakav prijatelj, ne znam što god, neko savjetnik?

175
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam Mario, nisam imao agenta, sve za mene odlučio.

176
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odlučio ekip, predsednik klub.

177
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Predsednik kluba.

178
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I imao je neki sportski direktor, da.

179
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, prilikom ovog transfera iz Makedonije u Inter, ti zapravo nemaš nikoga s kim bi porazgovarao, nego si faktički u rukama predsednika koji odlučio tvoje sodbenje.

180
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako.

181
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, da, ona, i to...

182
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako gledamo danas, da se događa, to je ne mogu.

183
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, danas je klinac od 8 godina, imao više menadžera.

184
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] To sve se promene.

185
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, za mene odlučio je klub i moj kući.

186
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mama, govori, šta ćeš u Milano, šta Inter, kao ti treba da završiš školo, još nisam završio sredno, ti treba da ideš u školo.

187
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tata volio futbal, tata volio puno futbala.

188
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači on je bio vaga, da.

189
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] A govori, ajde, neka proba malim, možda ga vratio, deće on u Inter, znaš, u malim.

190
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vratit će se za godinu danas, sigurno.

191
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nisu voditelji uopće, s tebi nikakve očekivanja nabijali?

192
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, nikad nisam imao od moj pritisak, zato što kad sam igrao u ove mlade kategorije,

193
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam ona, tata, nemoj da dolaziš, da gledaš.

194
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, jednostavno nije me ugodno da te gledam tamo kao da igra Goranso Privilegije.

195
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, igrao sam ja za postari.

196
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

197
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] I govori, neću, nemoj da dolaziš, govorim, bolje ti je sedi kućima.

198
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govori, neću dolaziš, ti stalno se kriva neko šta da, da gledaš u člijek i sa strane.

199
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazak u Inter iz Strumice, ovaj dio je meni jako interesanta, znači,

200
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] dolazak iz Strumice u Inter, iz jednog malog nogometnog mjestašca u jedan tako veliki klub.

201
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kakav je tvoj osjećaj u tom trenutku bio?

202
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer velika većina se izgubi igrača, klinaca, razmišljajući, to je to, wow, ja sam svoje napravio.

203
00:08:55,000 --> 00:09:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ne žele ići na posudbe, nego smatraju nerealno da u tom trenutku mogu konkurirati.

204
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, ti biraš totalno drugi put.

205
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti se vraćaš u speciju, u serije, to je bila ta treća liga.

206
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Treća liga, tako je.

207
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je u tom trenutku neko ti pomagao pri odluci?

208
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je, došao ja kao klinac u Milano.

209
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš da je Metropola 18 godina, klinac, potpisao za Inter.

210
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iako će sam imao te recim...

211
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako, predsednik mi je poklonio svake nedelje ili mesec da ne govori eva ti za da kupiš kopačke.

212
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam imao ugovor profesionalniji da uzmem platu.

213
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Posle, dolaziš ovde, napraviš ugovor 5 godina za klinac.

214
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ugovor, dolaziš u Milano 18 godina.

215
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja sam htio da živim u internat.

216
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi nađe profesor, imao sam profesor iz Srbije.

217
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šest meseci išao u školu.

218
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svako jutro me nosio u školu da govorim da moram da naučim jezik.

219
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Spavam tamo, jedem, treniram sve u bazu.

220
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja godinu dana...

221
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti recim na iskreno, nisam poznao ni jednu diskoteku u Milano.

222
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nedelj je bio dan da idem da gledam prvo ekipu.

223
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] To godine je bio Ronaldo.

224
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao Inter stvarno.

225
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stari Ronaldo.

226
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Luis Nazari odjelimo.

227
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki četvrtak išli su 4-5 klinice iz mladince u prvo ekipu.

228
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, svaki četvrtak odigraš neke utakmice sa neke iz četvrte, pete lige.

229
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stalno u prvo ekipu bio je...

230
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je još bio od igrača?

231
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio Cooper trener.

232
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio Cooper trener u prvo ekipu.

233
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

234
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio Sidorov.

235
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio Vieri.

236
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio Vieri.

237
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio Vieri.

238
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio Vieri Ronaldo.

239
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao Inter stvarno top ekipu.

240
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za strašujuću kvalitetu.

241
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan put, kad su zvali da idemo 4-5 u prvo ekipu, da treneraš da igraš sa Ronaldo.

242
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorim Goran, još ništa nisi ureda.

243
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treba još da radiš puno za da možeš da igraš na San Siro.

244
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad išš u nedelju da gledam utakmicu, bio je...

245
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moj san govorio da li mi se ostvari stan da igram ovde na San Siro.

246
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

247
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda donosiš odluku.

248
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čekaj, vratimo se malo za Ronaldo.

249
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je to najbolji igrač?

250
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Po moje, da.

251
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam trenirao sa prvo ekipu kada je on bio u top.

252
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa posle se povredio koleno.

253
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa posle, pred da se vrati na teren, došli su nama da trenira.

254
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] No dva meseci trenirao sa u Primaveru.

255
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] So mladinci i igrao sa nama u utakmicu.

256
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Igrao 3-4 utakmice da uđe.

257
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači Ronaldo nije bio problem da se vrati da igra za Primaveru.

258
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ronaldo je dolazio sa nama da odigrao tri utakmice.

259
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] I se sjećam dobro.

260
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je Vičenca dao je dva gola.

261
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazio si se ponašao, dao je ragaci.

262
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ste dečki, sve je dobro.

263
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Danas dobijemo, mora da dobijemo danas.

264
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to mi je ostaje.

265
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] To se desio pred 20 godina.

266
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je presnažna poruka.

267
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali se sjećaš, stvarno je bio...

268
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam igrao protiv njega i za mene je...

269
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Momak strašan, ta top.

270
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I žao mi je bio što je puno imao povrđa.

271
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali bio kod čoveka je bio stvarno...

272
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Za nama mladi je bio pravi primjer.

273
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Motivirajući primjer.

274
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, tako je.

275
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sama činjenica da se vratio, da igrao za mlađe je ono...

276
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, a nismo imali, stvarno nismo imali vrhunsku mladinsku ekipu.

277
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima Martins igrao napred.

278
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Osvojili smo posle 25 godina Inter mladinci osvoju skudeto.

279
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Skudeto.

280
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo dobili Viaređo.

281
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Viaređo je bio turniršta, jedan od najvažnijih turniru u Evropi.

282
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

283
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobili Viaređo.

284
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imali smo stvarno jako mladinsku ekipu.

285
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, ali donosiš odluku, vidiš da nemaš tu nečima dovoljna minutaža,

286
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] i odnosiš odluku da se vratiš i da igrao sa mladinske nogometri u speciji.

287
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako.

288
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam potpisao ogovor.

289
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi moj menadžer je bio Silvano Martina.

290
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Poznajem gospodin.

291
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da ga poznaš.

292
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Među ostalog i agent Bufona.

293
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bravo.

294
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ga poznaš, da.

295
00:12:57,000 --> 00:13:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] On je potpisao ovde sa njega i jedini što je pričao na naše.

296
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se razumemo, to je sve dobar na početak, da.

297
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on me zvao za u speciju, za treću ligu.

298
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja govorim, treću ligu u toj perioda je bio jaka liga.

299
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam 19 godina.

300
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pričao i direktora Intera govorio bolje.

301
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Išli od ove mladinske ekipa osam od nama u speciju.

302
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je imao 50% od akcije.

303
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gazda je bio Morati u speciju.

304
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nama šalio tamo.

305
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio kao sestrenski klub.

306
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bravo.

307
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

308
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nama osam šalio od ove ekipa što smo osvojili prvenstvo.

309
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šalio u treću ligu u speciju.

310
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mislim, za mene, to je bio pravi potek.

311
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da igraš so seniori.

312
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treću ligu je bio tuča, taktika.

313
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio pritisak.

314
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao puno specije.

315
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka utakmica imao po 15 idede ljudi.

316
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svake nedelje imao derby kao piza, kremoneze, karareze.

317
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ali velika većina igrača u tvojoj situaciji

318
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne bi uopće prihvatila da se vraća tri koraka ispod

319
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] i da ide u rizik da se vraća u treću ligu.

320
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je ta odluka fenomenalna jer je snažna i poruka.

321
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

322
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako je.

323
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je za mene bilo veliko iskuštvo.

324
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treću ligu.

325
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao i utakmice, stvarno su bili utakmice jače.

326
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ušao si ovaj nogomet u veliki nogomet.

327
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] So profesionalni...

328
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] So izgrađeni ljudima.

329
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] So izgrađeni ljudima koji znaju i tu.

330
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

331
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

332
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta imaš na publiku po 10.

333
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imali smo Piza, specija, 20.000 i bio u Piza.

334
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš opet neki pritisak, osjećaš...

335
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

336
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] ...adrenalina.

337
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] O mladinski form nismo bili šampioni.

338
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi samo menadžeri da gledaju i neki direktori iz kluba.

339
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I roditelji.

340
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo.

341
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo treću ligu.

342
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno mislim da sam dobio puno iskustva.

343
00:14:57,000 --> 00:15:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] i počeo više sam da razmišljam u profesionalnih futbola.

344
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da igraš na rezultata.

345
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ne idu stvari kao što je treba, ima prisa kod publiki,

346
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] kod navijače, kontestacijone, kako je pričao u Italiji.

347
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] I posle to zvao me Silvano Martina.

348
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorim imaš ponudu Ancona, Serie A.

349
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Čoveče, kako, Serie A?"

350
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Serie Č?"

351
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Idemo Serie B pa posle Serie A?"

352
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Ma ne."

353
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Govorim Ancona.

354
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo što je ušlo u prvu ligu.

355
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Te traži.

356
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moj, ja mislim da treba da ideš."

357
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti misliš da treba da idem.

358
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema nikakv problem.

359
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja mislim da još nisam spreman za Serie A.

360
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dalje si skroman i dalje si znači...

361
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

362
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja išu u Anconi.

363
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti recim na iskreno.

364
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znao sam da na početak da neću nikad igrati.

365
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što vidim ja imao Gantz.

366
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao Ubner.

367
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imao Pogi.

368
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači je isto snažna momča, da.

369
00:15:56,000 --> 00:16:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, imao momčada što su više imali pod 150-200 utakmice u Serie A.

370
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

371
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] U Serie A.

372
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja išao na pripreme sve dobro.

373
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, klinač ideš, ti trčiš sto puta više od svije.

374
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Borba, borba, borba.

375
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja nikad prvi osamnaest kola sve sam bio na tribini.

376
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš da ranije smo išli osamnaest na klupin.

377
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, 18 je bilo ono vrijeme.

378
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bilo toliki rostvar kao na klupin moguće.

379
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Išli u karantinu.

380
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nama ponese 20.

381
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja i drugi klinac, treći golman, idemo na tribini.

382
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jao, 18 utakmice na tribini.

383
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što se događa u tih trenutima?

384
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne padaš u depresiju?

